==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Table-land
<hw>Ta"ble-land`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A broad, level,
elevated area of land; a plateau.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The toppling crags of Duty scaled,⟦br⟧
Are close upon the shining <qex>table-lands</qex>⟦br⟧
To which our God himself is moon and sun.</q>
<rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tableman</ent>⟦br⟧
